Require agentgrep

Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-help.gif
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-help.mp4
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-help.webm

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 1080
Source docs/_static/demos/vhs/_preamble.tape

Sleep 1s
Type "agentgrep --help"
Enter
Wait
Sleep 3s
